# Repo scope guard.
#
# This git repo is rooted at $HOME (not by design — it should have lived
# inside a project folder). It only ever intended to track the Jenny
# Floreria planning docs below. Everything else in $HOME is ignored by
# default so a stray `git add -A` / `git add .` from the home directory
# can never sweep up SSH keys, credentials, or unrelated project files
# into this remote (github.com/vidadeloso/vida-del-oso-docs, which is PUBLIC).
#
# Already-tracked files are unaffected by this file — it only blocks new
# files from being added by accident.
/*
!/docs/
!/README.md
!/.gitignore
